        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-12-08T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-12-08T13:00:00-05:00" n="306" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d306">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">835.00/12–745: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cabot</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-12-08T13:00:00-05:00">December 8, 1945—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1746. Urtel 3062 Dec 7.<note n="72" xml:id="d306fn72">Not printed.</note> Full
                    details and documentary proof (if discreetly obtainable) of plans developed in
                    Police Dept for systemized anti-Semitic campaign of violence would be extremely
                    useful in preparation of our case here. Please telegraph whether these data are
                    likely to become available with reasonable promptness.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
